{
  "stem": "7093.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the camp commandant Hoess came, and the camp Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Mengele came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they-- we had to pass in front of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they waved us right and left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we, we had to show them our palm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And sometimes they said, open your mouth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- but otherwise, that's why we had to stand for 14 hours naked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they, they didn't-- anybody who collapsed, of course, was taken away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was, that was finished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then we-- I was taken into a row.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were led away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Yes, we were led out of the Birkenau B camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were led into another part, which was Auschwitz A, which we found out it was Auschwitz A.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there we had to-- we could sit down there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it got-- well, it was dark by that time, by the time we got there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then suddenly we smelled some-- we were smelling some beautiful cabbage soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then someone came around in the dark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "No, before-- sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Before that they took us again into this big hall and shaved us once more.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then gave us some clothing and-- fresh clothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And no, before they gave us fresh clothing, they started tattooing us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the tattooing, about 20 of us were tattooed and then there was an air raid.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a number that was tattooed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't have a number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the reason-- I have a number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have got it on every document which came out of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I haven't got an actual number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never have been tattooed because after 20 of us were about tattooed, there was an air raid.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was an air raid on the Buna Works, on the I.G.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
